Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.30,0:23:22.96,ED CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,400)}即便是看不見明天的夜晚
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.60,0:23:29.05,ED CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,400)}也會用心靈呼喚你
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.90,0:23:34.20,ED CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,400)}Please,stay with me
